{"tid":2782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]我細妹中三 就俾人搞大咗個肚","createTime":"2016-11-26T02:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T15:01:37.000Z","uid":3942,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"289797a906edcaf8c3961a4a8f4e9d8f60250d14","tid":2782,"uid":3942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:19:18.000Z","msg":"我細妹中三 就俾人搞大咗個肚... <br />\n<br />\n因為我細妹本身好MK 我又要番學 根本冇時間管佢既生活 <br />\n<br />\n其實我地屋企從細到大都係咁 <br />\n<br />\n阿爸阿媽番工 放假就係屋企休息 基本上我地兩兄妹只要唔變壞就唔會去管我地 <br />\n<br />\n但係我細妹呢件事太大獲 阿媽激到想辭職留係屋企 管我細妹 <br />\n<br />\n大概係3~4個月前 我細妹佢玩game識到一個男人 <br />\n<br />\n然後果個男人咁岩又住係我地附近 <br />\n<br />\n年紀應該有3X歲 而且離過婚 聽講離婚係因為經常飲醉酒發酒癲 <br />\n<br />\n佢地好似係網上傾咗2~3個禮拜就見面了 <br />\n<br />\n而且第一日見面就上佢屋企啪啪啪了 <br />\n<br />\n之後每個假日 佢地都會見面上佢度啪啪啪 <br />\n<br />\n就係咁一直持續了3個月左右 <br />\n<br />\n我細妹就同果個男人說講 她已經3個月冇黎m <br />\n<br />\n果個男人一開始話佢會負責 會黎我地屋企提親 <br />\n<br />\n估唔到講完呢句話 第二天就人間蒸發 手機都打不通 一直熄機 <br />\n<br />\n直到我細妹前日同我阿爸阿媽講呢件事 <br />\n<br />\n我爸媽前日夜晚12點 就衝去果個男人屋企撞門 <br />\n<br />\n要果個男人講清楚 而且準備告佢 果個男人話佢消失果兩個禮拜 係同朋友出國玩 <br />\n<br />\n咁岩今日番黎 準備要打俾我細妹 我地就衝咗過黎 <br />\n<br />\n我爸媽根本唔信 而且果個男人睇落窮酸樣 又住公屋 邊有錢出國玩 <br />\n<br />\n我細妹就一直喊一直喊 <br />\n<br />\n果晚我阿媽俾咗枝驗孕棒俾我細妹用 真係大咗肚 <br />\n<br />\n琴晚我知道咗件事之後 請咗一日假 同我細妹傾下 <br />\n<br />\n我細妹就話果個男人對佢好好 點點點咁 <br />\n<br />\n我根本就聽唔入耳 我就話 對你好 只不過係想呃你隻豬 <br />\n<br />\n一講完呢句 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我細妹就喊 然後將枱面部iPhone7掟落地 成個moon爆咗 <br />\n<br />\n所以我想下各位巴打 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知邊度整番個moon好 <br />\n<br />\nTHX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a92649cb2bf478f3164946a2915adc6eb04859","tid":2782,"uid":9863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:20:00.000Z","msg":"直接碌到最底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681655237228b465c73180e997d16eb3e65f8bdb","tid":2782,"uid":7567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:20:47.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，呢到係人都睇過呢篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f2b63d8f5ae59d1cb97d3c35c424f2f89e4eaf","tid":2782,"uid":11791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:20:53.000Z","msg":"出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b79beae82def50ae5b322240833d276c23266f","tid":2782,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:21:03.000Z","msg":"變左iphone7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ad02217076faf893efc484071edbc24a486ffc","tid":2782,"uid":6290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:22:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>變左iphone7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f049fbd207a47aa1796cfe40ee13bbef9bbe8df8","tid":2782,"uid":3942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:22:54.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打知去邊度整moon好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac920aa2c351b9d969006f5f0b7385e88015d1d","tid":2782,"uid":78,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:24:25.000Z","msg":"回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d5cb9fef3d6b026c8618633622dee60a1a748a","tid":2782,"uid":12332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:27:26.000Z","msg":"乜鳩整moon:0)"},{"pid":"c047f8dae4587c026fed2856d51b8eb4a198d3a2","tid":2782,"uid":14545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T02:28:07.000Z","msg":"幾多年前睇過呢篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce