normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩叫又回帶<br />\nLihkg第一篇爆moon潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bac0f837ccfcb894813457dab4175db397b054f","tid":2782,"uid":875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打知去邊度整moon好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶你細妺去揾一揾專業人士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢依家好需要人幫 唔好理其他嘢住啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之前都試過 叫係有啲經驗 呢啲最緊要揾最好嘅 但如果你budget有限就出旺角啦 好嘅我推介你去天才吧 嗰到啲人好pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acff9b0cfb7bcaeddf7b60e1ede253c86017ee37","tid":2782,"uid":7805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426e538665d1c227ad1d1e8683fcbb4acfbf764c","tid":2782,"uid":7367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"冇圖好難幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />lm"},{"pid":"59f585bc4857fdb35dfbb339025ad4d9a51f5462","tid":2782,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325571df456d37a9c63020c28bee18941a8262d0","tid":2782,"uid":6540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf16332d60beb8805d0fda5b8a4e586b5dc22221","tid":2782,"uid":8850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T03:43:09.000Z","msg":"心諗：咁熟口面既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji